Embed Code
Place the following code inside of the Quarto Document:
&lt;style&gt;
.slide-deck {
    border: 3px solid #dee2e6;
    width: 100%;
    height: 475px;
}
&lt;/style&gt;

&lt;div&gt;
```{=html}
&lt;iframe class="slide-deck" src="path/to/presentation/"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
```
&lt;/div&gt;
